title: These Are The BEST Wireless Gaming Headsets!
description: We set out of find the absolute BEST wireless gaming headset that combines comfort, price, audio performance and mic quality.  Headsets from Corsair, Logitech, Razer, Steelseries and HyperX were tested and we actually came to some surprising conclusions.      Buy items in this video from Amazon at the links below:  Corsair VOID Pro:   Logitech G533:   Arctis 7:   Logitech G933 Artemis:   Razer Man 'O War:   HyperX Cloud Flight:   Razer Thresher:   Arctis Pro Wireless:    OCZ TR200 SSD (Sponsor):    Dmitry's Lamp:    Individual Reviews:    Void Pro:   Logitech G533:   Arctis 7:   HyperX Cloud Flight:   Arctis Pro + GameDac:   Subscribe    Review unit provided free of charge by the companies mentioned. This video is sponsored by OCZ. As per HWC guidelines, no review direction was received from manufacturer.   As an Amazon Associate we earn from qualifying purchases.  Gear list (buy from Amazon):  Panasonic GH5 -  Panasonic GH4 -  Panasonic G7 -  Canon C100 -  Sony RX100m3 -  Sigma 18-35mm F1.8 -  Cinevate DUZI Slider -  AKG C314 -  AKG C 568 B -  Zoom H5 -  ------------------------------------------------------------ Our full site:  Join Our Forums:   Follow us for more updates!
